EXERCISE 14 - employeeapp | HOL 14: React Context API
============================================================
Category  : Additional Important
Topic     : createContext(), Provider, useContext(), theme sharing
App Name  : employeeapp
Status    : COMPLETED ✅

------------------------------------------------------------
CONTEXT API IMPLEMENTATION
------------------------------------------------------------
  1. createContext()
     const ThemeContext = createContext('light');

  2. Provider (App component wraps the tree)
     <ThemeContext.Provider value={theme}>
       <EmployeeList />
     </ThemeContext.Provider>

  3. Consumer (EmployeeCard reads theme without props)
     const theme = useContext(ThemeContext);
     → No prop drilling needed!

  4. Theme toggle
     useState('light') → button toggles 'light'/'dark'

